summary.label:
Dont Forgeter is a lightning-fast, clear and efficient to-do list that will keep you up-to-date with all the important stuff. We have designed it to be as fast as possible so that you won't waste your time on additional gestures and actions anymore.

Key features:

- add to-do's with only one word thanks to our new suggestion system;
- add reminders with one swipe and plan your days, weeks, or even months with no efforts at all;
- add as many reminders for one to-do as you want - the main thing is that you don't forget;
- control your life on the go with easy-to-manage lists and one-hand navigation system, perfect for intensive and busy lifestyle.

This app is designed for people who do not want to waste even 2 or 3 additional seconds for creating to-dos and reminders. It is a perfect choice for those who live very fast and really want to catch all the chances the life brings.

Save your time and never forget anything again!
